metadata.name: Resistance boy #1
metadata.description: In the Metaverse –ên unnamed disease kills half of humanity and turns the remaining half into zombie-like creatures. The government ordered everyone who survived to wear a mask to prevent spreading the virus and anyone who disobeyed was killed. In a small city near Denver is created a group of survivors called the resistance who believe that the government is trying to control the people and refuse to wear a mask. They will try to take down the government and help people have their old life back. Which side will you take? The government or the resistance?
